FluxPlayer

STATES:
- Current playing song
    - Init (Song previously played, if exists)
    - Playing song.
    - Song stopped.
    - Song paused.
    - Time updated.
    - Next Song.
    - Preview Song.

- Queue
    - Init queue.
    - Play song.
    - Add song to queue.
    - Remove song from queue.
    - Change song position.
    - Mark as favorite.

https://github.com/Yarikx/reductor
